            "title": "盤中速報 - 欣新網(2949)急拉4.67%報65.0元，成交1張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>欣新網(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2949:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2949\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2949-TW</a>)近5分K漲速4.67%，29日13:03報65.0元，成交1張，今日漲幅為0.15％。（註：漲跌速為5分K的漲跌幅）</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>欣新網(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2949:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2949\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2949-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌0.15%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-2 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-2 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
